  {
    "id": "eq-us7000t1bu",
    "title": "為墨西哥地震平安祈福",
    "event": "2026 年 7 月 17 日，墨西哥外海（Puerto Madero 西南方約 58 公里）發生規模 7.3 強震，願當地居民平安、家園早日復原。",
    "sources": [
      {
        "ref": "USGS 地震資訊",
        "url": "https://earthquake.usgs.gov/earthquakes/eventpage/us7000t1bu"
      },
      {
        "ref": "交通部中央氣象署地震測報中心",
        "url": "https://scweb.cwa.gov.tw/zh-tw/earthquake/data"
      }
    ],
    "place": "58 km WSW of Puerto Madero, Mexico",
    "mag": 7.3,
    "lat": 14.6043,
    "lon": -92.9517,
    "time": "2026-07-17",
    "since": "2026-07-17",
    "status": "memorial",
    "updates": [
      {
        "date": "2026-07-17",
        "text": "恰帕斯州州長召開擴大內閣會議，協調各單位評估震損並強化跨部門應變，以保障居民安全。",
        "sources": [
          {
            "ref": "El Congresista",
            "url": "https://elcongresista.mx/politica/chiapas/despliegue-seguridad-sismo-chiapas-julio-2026"
          }
        ],
        "added": "2026-07-20T04:51:59.125Z",
        "hash": "2a35780148c8"
      },
      {
        "date": "2026-07-19",
        "text": "墨西哥恰帕斯州當局初步勘查地震災情，指出部分民宅、學校、醫療站與宗教場所出現結構受損，各級政府持續派員赴災區複勘。",
        "sources": [
          {
            "ref": "N+ (nmas.com.mx)",
            "url": "https://www.nmas.com.mx/chiapas/sociedad/hubo-danos-sismo-chiapas-7-4-autoridades-informan-como-estan-municipios-estado/"
          }
        ],
        "added": "2026-07-20T04:51:58.124Z",
        "hash": "51864a0df0cf"
      },
      {
        "date": "2026-07-21",
        "text": "恰帕斯州官方持續複勘後正式公布受損鄉鎮範圍，部分住宅經評估列為不可居住，當地持續進行後續安置與處置。",
        "sources": [
          {
            "ref": "Proceso",
            "url": "https://www.proceso.com.mx/nacional/estados/2026/7/21/sismos-en-chiapas-dejan-danos-en-17-municipios-reportan-22-viviendas-inhabitables-376517.html"
          }
        ],
        "added": "2026-07-21T12:31:05.307Z",
        "hash": "8ae6885ee915"
      }
    ],
    "followup": {
      "sealed": false,
